name: BigUint64Array.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 8 in the case of BigUint64Array.

name: BigUint64Array.prototype.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 8 in the case of a BigUint64Array.

name: BigUint64Array.prototype.constructor
description: The constructor function that created the instance object. For BigUint64Array instances, the initial value is the BigUint64Array constructor.
